            <title>心……痛</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_472b64f90100i3e7.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><font SIZE="3"><a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/472b64f9t86a4a0e0812a" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/472b64f9t86a4a0e0812a&amp;690" WIDTH="690" HEIGHT="459" /></A><br />
<br />
<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/472b64f9t86a4a13c024d" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/472b64f9t86a4a13c024d&amp;690" WIDTH="459" HEIGHT="690" /></A><br />
