            <title>丹哥荣摘魅力年度男演员奖</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_472b64f90100c9k6.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 12px">3<font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">月11日，香港专业电影摄影师学会21周年庆典晚宴在香港尖沙咀举办，<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: DFKai-SB; mso-hansi-font-family: DFKai-SB; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 12px"><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">所有会员都是专业电影摄影师，</FONT><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">丹哥获摘<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: DFKai-SB; mso-hansi-font-family: DFKai-SB; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">最具魅力年度男演员奖！！</FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<p><a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/472b64f9g650eb7569431" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/472b64f9g650eb7569431" /></A></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p>丹哥日前出席为香港电影诞辰一百周年举办的<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">《影·话·百年》活动，丹哥<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">并担任了《影·话·百年》的电影大使。</SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
