<p>丹哥与众电影人<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">分享了拍电影的心得</SPAN></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/472b64f9g650abaeae833" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/472b64f9g650abaeae833" /></A></P>
